reviewText: This is a documentary with alot of interviews of Dick Drost.  The event itself is fantastic and well shot , this contest continued well into the 80's and covered superbly by companies like Girlie Video and Dale Zunz productions.

Do not buy this movie for a plot line.  It is more about ego and the girls walking around.  The women are very pretty and natural.  Buy it only if you want to see shots of women who look natural.  I think this was the first movie in this series and a bit less contrived than more current ones.
